# Discord Bot Token
# Get your token from https://discord.com/developers/applications > Bot section
# Click "Reset Token" - use ONLY the part AFTER the first dot (not the numbers before it)
# Example: if token is "123456.abcdefgh...", use only "abcdefgh..."
DISCORD_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here

# Required Bot Permissions (when inviting):
# - Send Messages
# - Embed Links
# - Read Message History
# - Use External Emojis
# - Server Members Intent (enable in Discord Developer Portal > Bot > Privileged Gateway Intents)
# - Message Content Intent (enable in Discord Developer Portal > Bot > Privileged Gateway Intents)
